claim: Adrianne Palicki turned down a supporting role in John Wick.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Adrianne Lee Palicki  (  born May 6 , 1983  )  is an American actress best known for her roles as Tyra Collette in the television series Friday Night Lights  (  2006 -- 2011  )  and supporting roles in the films Legion  (  2010  )  , Red Dawn  (  2012  )  , G.I. Joe : Retaliation  (  2013  )  , and John Wick  (  2014  )  .
